OL,3,CTories promise to expand triple lock
OL,4,Cgiving pensioners #2.4bn income tax
OL,5,Cbreak
OL,7,FPensioners will be given a tax break
OL,8,Fworth #2.4 billion a year, Rishi Sunak
OL,9,Fis expected to promise as part of an
OL,10,Fexpansion of the triple lock.
OL,12,FThe prime minister will announce on
OL,13,FTuesday that from April next year the
OL,14,Fincome tax personal allowance for
OL,15,Fpensioners will be increased in line
OL,16,Fwith the triple lock, as he continues
OL,17,Fthe Conservatives' election campaign.
