OL,3,CTories promise to expand triple lock
OL,4,Cgiving pensioners #2.4bn income tax
OL,5,Cbreak
OL,7,FThe pledge would mean both the state
OL,8,Fpension and pensioners' tax-free
OL,9,Fallowance will always rise in line
OL,10,Fwith the highest of earnings, wages or
OL,11,F2.5%.
OL,13,FBilled the "triple lock plus," the
OL,14,Fpolicy is estimated to cost #2.4
OL,15,Fbillion a year by 2029/30, a price tag
OL,16,Fwhich mirrors Mr Sunak's proposed
OL,17,Fnational service duty for all 18-year-
OL,18,Folds, billed at #2.5 billion a year.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/9
