OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F313A1716907732
OL,3,CTories promise to expand triple lock
OL,4,Cgiving pensioners #2.4bn income tax
OL,5,Cbreak
OL,7,FThe tax cut will be funded through a
OL,8,Fpreviously announced plan to raise #6
OL,9,Fbillion a year by the end of the next
OL,10,Fparliament by clamping down on tax
OL,11,Favoidance and evasion.
OL,13,FFor individual pensioners, it would be
OL,14,Fworth around #100 in 2025 according to
OL,15,Fthe Tories, and would grow over time,
OL,16,Fadding to their incomes on top of
OL,17,Frises in the state pension.
