OL,3,CTories promise to expand triple lock
OL,4,Cgiving pensioners #2.4bn income tax
OL,5,Cbreak
OL,7,FThe policy follows criticism of
OL,8,FChancellor Jeremy Hunt's decision to
OL,9,Fcut national insurance by 2p at the
OL,10,Fspring budget, after a similar cut in
OL,11,Fthe autumn.
OL,13,FState pensioners did not benefit from
OL,14,Fthe cut, as they do not pay national
OL,15,Finsurance.
