OL,3,CTories promise to expand triple lock
OL,4,Cgiving pensioners #2.4bn income tax
OL,5,Cbreak
OL,7,FWhile Mr Sunak said the Tories were
OL,8,Fcommitted to the triple lock, he
OL,9,Fclaimed Labour would by contrast drag
OL,10,Fpensioners in receipt of the full
OL,11,Fstate pension "into income tax for the
OL,12,Ffirst time in history".
OL,14,FThe prime minister said: "I
OL,15,Fpassionately believe that those who
OL,16,Fhave worked hard all their lives
OL,17,Fshould have peace of mind and security
OL,18,Fin retirement.
