OL,3,CTories promise to expand triple lock
OL,4,Cgiving pensioners #2.4bn income tax
OL,5,Cbreak
OL,7,F"Thanks to the Conservatives' triple
OL,8,Flock, pensions have risen by #900 this
OL,9,Fyear and now we will cut their taxes
OL,10,Fby around #100 next year.
OL,12,F"This bold action demonstrates we are
OL,13,Fon the side of pensioners. The
OL,14,Falternative is Labour dragging
OL,15,Feveryone in receipt of the full state
OL,16,Fpension into income tax for the first
OL,17,Ftime in history."
OL,19,FBut Labour claimed the Tories' offer
OL,20,Fto pensioners was not credible.
