OL,3,CTories promise to expand triple lock
OL,4,Cgiving pensioners #2.4bn income tax
OL,5,Cbreak
OL,7,F"Why would anyone believe the Tories
OL,8,Fand Rishi Sunak on tax after they left
OL,9,Fthe country with the highest tax
OL,10,Fburden in 70 years?" said Jonathan
OL,11,FAshworth, the shadow paymaster general.
OL,13,FHe added: "This is just another
OL,14,Fdesperate move from a chaotic Tory
OL,15,FParty torching any remaining facade of
OL,16,Fits claims to economic credibility.
