OL,3,CTories promise to expand triple lock
OL,4,Cgiving pensioners #2.4bn income tax
OL,5,Cbreak
OL,7,F"Not only have they promised to spend
OL,8,Ftens of billions of pounds since this
OL,9,Fcampaign began, they also have a
OL,10,Fcompletely unfunded #46 billion policy
OL,11,Fto scrap national insurance that
OL,12,Fthreatens the very basis of the state
OL,13,Fpension.
OL,15,F"Labour will protect the triple lock.
OL,16,FBut Rishi Sunak is planning to reward
OL,17,FBritain's pensioners for their loyalty
OL,18,Fby stabbing them in the back, just
OL,19,Flike he did to Boris Johnson and just
OL,20,Flike he has done to his own MPs."
